data.text:
Parking and Directions

We have approximately 140 parking places around the church and in our church parking lot. Visitor spots are marked in the lot behind the church. Enter the parking lot on 4th Street.

Handicapped parking can be found on Broad Street in front of the Church as well as on 4th Street. A handicap ramp is located on the 4th Street door of the church.

There is additional parking available on Broad Street, 3rd Street, and 4th Street. There are also auxiliary parking lots available at Northwestern Human Services, Community Housing, and the US Gas Station.
